  m_text: 'The image depicts a cartoon-style scene of a man and a llama sitting on
    furniture in a living room. The man sits on a white couch wearing a blue jacket
    over a white shirt, dark pants, and sneakers. He looks at the llama with his
    right hand raised in a gesture. The llama sits on a chair opposite him, with
    light-brown fur and a cream-colored belly. Its right arm rests on the chair''s
    back while its left arm mirrors the man''s gesture. A small table with white
    objects and a lamp shade are nearby, set against an orange-yellow gradient background.



'
